---
import ImgAboutUs from "../../assets/images/img-about-us.png"
import ImgAboutUsMobile from "../../assets/images/img-about-us-mobile.png"
---

<section
  id="2"
  class="section about scroll-mt-16 px-6 pb-12 lg:flex lg:gap-x-10 lg:pl-0 lg:pb-[120px] lg:scroll-mt-[108px]"
>
  <div class="w-auto max-w-[55%]">
    <img src={ImgAboutUs} alt="img-about-us" class="hidden lg:block" />
  </div>
  <div class="xl:max-w-[496px]">
    <h6
      class="font-bold font-manjari text-lg text-neutral-2 text-center leading-[140%] xl:text-[32px] lg:text-start"
    >
      About Us
    </h6>
    <h1
      class="font-gothic text-[32px] text-center leading-[140%] xl:text-[52px] lg:text-start"
    >
      Why You Should Choose Adlova
    </h1>
    <img
      src={ImgAboutUsMobile}
      alt="img-about-us-mobile"
      class="mt-4 lg:hidden"
    />
    <p class="font-manjari text-neutral-1 my-4 xl:text-lg xl:my-6">
      We transform your brand into an unstoppable force in the digital world. We
      are passionate about driving your success and propelling your business to
      new heights through innovative strategies and cutting-edge solutions.
      <br />
      <br />
      At Adlova, we understand the power of effective marketing. With a team of experienced
      professionals, we specialize in creating customized campaigns that resonate
      with your target audience and deliver measurable results.
    </p>
    <span class="font-gothic text-primary-2 cursor-pointer xl:text-lg"
      >Read More...</span
    >
  </div>
</section>
